<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{{2}{a}^{{2}}-{16}{a}+{73}}}{{{a}^{{2}}-{8}{a}-{9}}}-\frac{{{a}^{{2}}+{a}+{1}}}{{{a}^{{2}}-{8}{a}-{9}}}=</m><fillin characters="20" /> Â 

