<solution>
<p><ul><li><m>\displaystyle\frac{{{a}-{8}}}{{{a}+{1}}}</m></li></ul></p><p>Since the denominators are the same, we can subtract the numerators:
</p><tabular>
  <row><cell><m>\displaystyle\frac{{{2}{a}^{{2}}-{16}{a}+{73}}}{{{a}^{{2}}-{8}{a}-{9}}}-\frac{{{a}^{{2}}+{a}+{1}}}{{{a}^{{2}}-{8}{a}-{9}}}</m></cell><cell><m>\displaystyle=</m></cell><cell><m>\displaystyle\frac{{{\left({2}{a}^{{2}}-{16}{a}+{73}\right)}-{\left({a}^{{2}}+{a}+{1}\right)}}}{{{a}^{{2}}-{8}{a}-{9}}}</m></cell><cell></cell></row>
  <row><cell></cell><cell><m>\displaystyle=</m></cell><cell><m>\displaystyle\frac{{{a}^{{2}}-{17}{a}+{72}}}{{{a}^{{2}}-{8}{a}-{9}}}</m></cell></row>
  <row><cell>We can try to factor numerator and denominator to simplify:</cell></row>
  <row><cell></cell><cell><m>\displaystyle=</m></cell><cell><m>\displaystyle\frac{{{\left({a}-{8}\right)}{\left({a}-{9}\right)}}}{{{\left({a}+{1}\right)}{\left({a}-{9}\right)}}}</m></cell></row>
  <row><cell>Then remove the common factor:</cell></row>
  <row><cell></cell><cell><m>\displaystyle=</m></cell><cell><m>\displaystyle\frac{{{a}-{8}}}{{{a}+{1}}}</m></cell></row>
</tabular>
</solution>
